  <title>Intruder and presence detection</title>

  <section>
    <title>System sensors</title>

    <para>The living space of the ship is monitored exclusively by a
    collection of passive infrared (PIR) presence detectors.</para>

    <informaltable>
      <tgroup cols="3">
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>1</entry>

            <entry>Master cabin</entry>

